# API routes

- Export named HTTP handlers (`GET`, `POST`, …) from `route.ts` files.
- Validate request bodies; prefer Zod or typed guards (see `src/app/api/contact/route.ts`).
- Use `@/utils/logger` for server logging instead of bare `console.log` in new code.
- Secrets via `config.get()` from `@/lib/config` where applicable.
- Return `NextResponse.json()` with appropriate status codes.
- CORS headers are set globally in `next.config.js` for `/api/*`.
- AI chat: provider chain in `@/services/ai/orchestrator`; config in `@/lib/ai-config`.
- TTS: orchestrator and providers under `@/services/tts/`.
